snippet.title: Daredevil Dave: Motorcycle Stuntman! - For iPhone
snippet.description:
Introducing Daredevil Dave, by M-Digital Media. For iPhone, iPod Touch and iPad. Although the goal is to land the jumps, crashing is so much more fun!!! 

Stay tuned for the sequel to this hit game! Should be sometime this summer! 

http://www.mdigitalmedia.com
